Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sweetie Belle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe we should run\Nthrough the steps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,another few times before\Nyou try it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Ready to give\Nit a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,OK then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't seem to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! I think I threw\Nmy neck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, you're OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more magic practice and\Nlifting brooms'll be a cinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing weighs a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, has anypony\Nhere seen my--?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. I'll never get my\Ncutie mark for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm happy to keep\Nhelping you learn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,just for the fun of\Nit as long you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who's gonna\Nclean up this mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the carefully\Narranged pieces of a unicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I took apart and will be\Nputting back together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as Twilight\Nshows me how.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo, I already told\Nyou I won't show you how.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll help you\Nfind the instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can figure\Nit out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Blech, I hate research.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To your left, third\Nshelf from the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much for\Nhelping us all learn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,these new skills, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Always glad to pass on my love\Nof learning for learning's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I'm afraid I'll never get\Nthe hang of this potion-making.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you follow the magic\Nplant-growing formula
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's try it out\Non this apple seedling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and see how we do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I hope this works!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Laying it on a little\Nthick there, aren't we, pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yoohoo! Gather round!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As you all know, I had\Npromised to put on an amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,first-time-ever acrobatic\Ndisplay for you all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. It's so exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did not wish\Nto disappoint you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so I brought my butler\NRandolph to do them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing,\NDiamond Tiara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I don't\Nknow how I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she\Ngets so much attention
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,without even really\Ndoing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's using somepony\Nelse to build herself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And without even putting in the\Neffort to learn her own skills
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,like we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if we get really\Ngood at the stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight's teaching us, we could\Nbe the big shots around here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,for a change. Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And check this out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can't you\Nhear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asking if your sister\NRarity will be taking you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to Manehattan anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if she is, maybe\Nyou can meet up with us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,while we hang out with a\Nbunch of famous celebrities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's pretty\Nnice of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, my sister\Nhasn't offered to take me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to Manehattan anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bump. Bump. Sugarlump. Rump.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Well, I don't have to\Ngo all the way to Manehattan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to hang out with the famous\Nand super-cool ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and my friends hang out with\NPrincess Twilight all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say\N"Princess Twilight?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You hang out with\Nher all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,More like just once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She helps us learn\Ncool new stuff to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That we actually do.\NOurselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You must bring me\Nalong next time you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring us along!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean we used to see{\i0}\N{\i1}her around town all the time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I thought whatever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. I thought that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But now she's a Princess, which\Nmakes her totally awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus she has wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's an Alicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think\Nwe should.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you two excuse\Nus for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We should totally say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a golden opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want them laughing at\Nus while I'm mixin' potions
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and accidentally sendin'\Nplants into choking fits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll have to\Nlearn something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And they won't be able to laugh\Nat us when they're so busy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to learn\Nstuff of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I must admit it's kinda fun\Nto see them working hard
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to get on our good\Nside for a change
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh my gosh, a princess{\i0}\N{\i1}lives in there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm about to go\Ninside and see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even tell\Nyou how excited I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now remember, Twilight takes\Nthis time out with us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can learn stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, guys!\NCome on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's really her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and uh, you\Nbrought guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight, it is such\Na thrill and honor to be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, who dyes your tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I so have to\Nget that done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's not dyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are those books in there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bold design choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You should so do that, Di.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. I'm all for helping\Nas many ponies as I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but maybe we should keep\Nthese weekly visits
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,just between us, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, which one of you\Nwants to practice first?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't they go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No silly, I set up Twilight\NTime especially for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Applebloom, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how your plant\Npotions are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I\Nlet you talk us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,into bringing\Nguests yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear them laugh\Nat us once, Applebloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they laughed\Non the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't make that\Nsame mistake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who showed up\Nto make fun of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for learning\Nskills to be big shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guess what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I told everyone about your\Nspecial Twilight time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And they all want in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Time! Twilight Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to me, you three are\Nnow the hottest thing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Time! Twilight Time!\NTwilight Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight time! Twilight time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! All these ponies really\Nwant to meet Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you, Cutie\NMark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now now, everypony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Demanding time with a\NPrincess as an unruly mob
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,simply won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Might I suggest you get\Norganized through us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the Cutie Mark Crusaders'\Nnearest and dearest friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony get in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No pushing. No pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see? We're really\Nand truly and certifiably
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the biggest of the bigshots\Nin school right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They all think\Nwe're the greatest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're their\Nticket to get time with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville's newest and biggest\Ncelebrity: Princess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We just said like two seconds\Nago that inviting two ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to Twilight Time\Nwas a big mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and now we're supposed to{\i0}\N{\i1}bring the whole class?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this,\NSweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You said not to invite them\Nto Twilight Time and I didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels like a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's tricky about inviting\NTwilight out for a meal
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,thanking her for all the nice\Nthings she's done for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like the least\Nwe can do for the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone say Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told you when you could\Ncome eyeball the Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,at one of her favorite hangouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I said only two or\Nthree of you, tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oops.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, but stay out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. As I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmm. Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize\Nhow hungry I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you asked\Nme to join you here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first asked me to\Nhelp you develop new skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought: working with young\Nstudents so devoted to the joy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of learning purely\Nfor its own sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What could be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You all remind me of\Nmyself when I was your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, we feel\Nthe same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we invited you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of our love\Nof learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Twilight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen you here in,\Nlike, forever-and-a-half!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so busy I forgot how\Ndelicious everything is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on\Nout there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind. They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ La la la la la. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is\Ngoing on out--?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What was all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I don't smile in\Na picture, I look sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're gonna\Nlook sad all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get my picture\Nwith her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get out of the shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight's gonna be\Nso ticked at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you this was\Na terrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You seriously all\Nwant my autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, I'll sign just a\Ncouple more for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but then I really must get\Nback to my little friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, to think I've been to the\NHay Burger so many times
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,never knowing it was the\Nregular hangout for a Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't my regular hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only here to be with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, Princess\NTwilight decides
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,where it's cool to go\Nbased on where they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha - ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks guys. This was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm opening a new\Nlemonade stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you come to the\Ngrand opening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you free\Nlemonade for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. I know exactly\Nhow to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yippee! Lemonade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,More lemonade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Done shining your hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to do\Nyou the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, so bright I can see myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And so can I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice job\Nbedazzling my bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I owe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gratitude is\Nthanks enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You three must come\Nto my pool party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be much\Ncooler than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's inviting\Nwho to her fancy house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe we have arrived,\NCutie Mark Crusaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is nice, but\Nthere's no one else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this party\Ncooler exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of all the\Nponies we're keeping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This has been great,\Nbut we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Twilight Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're coming\Ntoo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have a chance\Nto ask Twilight, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? After all the\Nfavors we did for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After all the favors\Nthey did for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Time! Twilight Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Time! Twilight Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. I know exactly\Nhow to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight time! Twilight time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to beat them to\NTwilight's so we can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This way. I know a short cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight time! Twilight time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we run...like the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it! Quick, knock on--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, we can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We know you said we should\Njust keep Twilight Time to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't mean for so many\Nother ponies to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I only meant that\Nfor your benefit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so you could get the most\Nout of our time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you want to share your\Ntime with others, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike made nachos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out we'll need\Nsome more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we start, we should\Nmaybe get a bit more organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies interested in\Nmagic in this corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies who want to learn\Npotions over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bookworm\Nponies over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like everything's\Nworking out just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was so afraid Twilight\Nwould be disappointed in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you I knew exactly\Nhow to handle all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to all of you\Nfor taking time out
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to come learn new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, OK, let's settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to thank anypony,\Nthank the Cutie Mark Crusaders
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for so generously{\i0}\N{\i1}sharing this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We just felt it was\Nthe right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And what would you like\Nto learn, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to learn how to\Nbecome a Cutie Mark Crusader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And why do you want to become\Na Cutie Mark Crusader so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because then I could get all my\Nclassmates to do me favors
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and stuff because I'm friends\Nwith a famous Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted our time together\Njust as a way to be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and learn new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Really and truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's true, then I'm sure\Nyou've all been practicing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,your skills over the past week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me how much better you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh well, uh, we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We kind of rushed over and\Nforgot to bring our stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey everypony, you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to learn,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but instead you're getting\Ndinner and a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready, 'cause we,\Nthe Cutie Mark Crusaders,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,are about to lay on\Nyou the amazing skills
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we learned in Twilight Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, since we don't\Nhave Scootaloo's unicycle parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll take apart and\Nput back together
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the scooters\Nfrom outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my scooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You got us into this mess, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Might wanna roll with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Applebloom doesn't have{\i0}\N{\i1}her apple seedling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so she'll just grab an{\i0}\N{\i1}apple from the kitchen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will begin by using\Nmy magic to lift this broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ta da! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Become a tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That didn't turn out\Nquite how I had hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Twilight\NTime is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And look who's not the\NPrincess' entourage anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oooooh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess they didn't come\Nhere to learn after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, neither did any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Awwwww.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really sorry, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We made a huge mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And we really and truly\Ndid enjoy learning
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,new skills with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll just have to keep\Non doing it without you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember a moment ago when you\Nasked me to "give you a chance?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Awww, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess Twilight must not{\i0}\N{\i1}be so super upset anymore{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'cause she's letting us do a{\i0}\N{\i1}diary entry like our sisters do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boy, did we get our{\i0}\N{\i1}priorities mixed up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We started acting special{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because we were friends{\i0}\N{\i1}with someone special.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We almost forgot the real{\i0}\N{\i1}reason she's special:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because she's our friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she forgave us and, like{\i0}\N{\i1}magic, things are good as new.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the kind of magic I{\i0}\N{\i1}really want to get good at...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}now that I'm getting so{\i0}\N{\i1}good at the other kind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, all three of you have\Nmade so much progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really proud of you!
